 r←Test_043(stopFlag batchFlag);⎕TRAP;path;zipFilename;targetFolder;myZip;src2;list2;list1;path2
⍝ Create a new Zip archive, add two files and an empty (!) directory
 ⎕TRAP←(999 'C' '∘∘∘ ⍝ Deliberate error')(0 'N')
